  "body": "`kube-apiserver` should have a concept of whether it is currently ready for connections or not. It could say not when it is shutting down, initializing, or disconnected from etcd. This can be checked by kubelet and fed to a load balancer to keep clients from attempting to connect to a replica which is not ready.\r\n\r\n#54849 adds a more graceful shutdown path, we should build on that.",
